title: What Does Adding Julio Mean?
description:
Domonique Foxworth, Pablo Torre, and Elle Duncan debate what signing Julio Jones does for Tom Brady and the Bucs, if the Vikings GM was too honest about Kirk Cousins, If it would be good for baseball if Shohei Ohtani gets traded to a good team, and what their reaction is to Kirk Ferentz saying college football needs and intervention.
